files.name: nav-list.component.ts
files.content: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { faChevronRight } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'; @Component({ // tslint:disable-next-line:component-selector selector: 'nav-list', templateUrl: './nav-list.component.html' }) export class NavListComponent { faChevronRight = faChevronRight; }

files.content: import { NgModule } from '@angular/core'; import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common'; import { NavListComponent } from './nav-list.component'; import { DaffListModule } from '@daffodil/design'; import { FontAwesomeModule } from '@fortawesome/angular-fontawesome'; @NgModule({ declarations: [ NavListComponent ], imports: [ CommonModule, DaffListModule, FontAwesomeModule ], exports: [ NavListComponent ] }) export class NavListModule { }
